<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>BCSO - Mise à jour système</title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;600;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #05070b;
            color: white;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            background-image: 
                radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(189, 165, 129, 0.05) 0%, transparent 70%),
                linear-gradient(rgba(189, 165, 129, 0.02) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(189, 165, 129, 0.02) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 100% 100%, 30px 30px, 30px 30px;
        }
        .maintenance-box {
            max-width: 650px;
            padding: 50px;
            background: rgba(11, 15, 25, 0.8);
            border: 1px solid rgba(189, 165, 129, 0.15);
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
        }
        .logo {
            width: 150px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            filter: drop-shadow(0px 0px 20px rgba(189, 165, 129, 0.3));
        }
        h1 {
            color: #bda581;
            font-size: 26px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        p {
            color: #cbd5e1;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .loader-container {
            margin-top: 35px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        .loader-icon {
            font-size: 28px;
            color: #bda581;
        }
        .auto-refresh-text {
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="maintenance-box">
        <img src="/images/bcso.png" alt="BCSO Logo" class="logo">
        <h1>Mise à jour en cours</h1>
        <p>Le système informatique du Blaine County Sheriff's Office est temporairement inaccessible. Une mise à jour importante de la base de données est en cours de déploiement.</p>
        
        <div class="loader-container">
            <i class="fas fa-circle-notch fa-spin loader-icon"></i>
            <span class="auto-refresh-text">Cette page s'actualisera automatiquement dès la remise en ligne du réseau.</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- SCRIPT TEMPS RÉEL SOCKET.IO -->
    <script src="/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>
    <script>
        const socket = io();
        
        // Si le super-admin coupe la maintenance, la page se recharge instantanément
        socket.on('maintenance-toggled', (isMaintenance) => {
            if (!isMaintenance) {
                window.location.reload(); 
            }
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>